document_data.mainbody: '''Sullen Street''' was a road located in the city of [[Zhentil Keep]] during the midâ€“14{{th}} century [[DR]].
document_data.Location: Sullen Street was located in south Zhentil Keep within the [[Zhentil Keep/Harbor District|Harbor District]] The road was located on the eastern side of the Harbor District. It originated at the wall to the [[Zhentil Keep/Common Quarter|Common Quarter]] then passed west to connect with [[Ocean Way]] near the docks.
document_data.Notable Locations: A [[Zhentarim]] warehouse was located along Sullen Street.
